Just stood up a fresh Fedora 43 VM, I'm seeing `bridge` as the driver.

Created caddy.unit:

```
[Container]
Image=docker.io/library/caddy
ContainerName=caddy-container
Network=caddy.network
```

caddy.network:

```
[Network]
```

Both installed in `~/.config/containers/systemd/`

```
$ systemctl --user daemon-reload
$ systemctl --user start caddy.service
$ podman network inspect systemd-caddy
